linux packages:
- nodejs, npm
- jq
- nginx
- neovim
- gh (GitHub CLI)
- direnv
- ripgrep

tmux layouts:
- even-horizontal (evenly spaced vertical panes)
- even-vertical (evenly spaced horizontal panes)
- main-horizontal (large top pane, smaller bottom panes)
- main-vertical (large left pane, smaller right panes)
- tiled (all panes same size in grid)

tmux layout commands:
- Ctrl-b : select-layout <layout-name>
- Ctrl-b Alt-1 (even-horizontal)
- Ctrl-b Alt-2 (even-vertical)
- Ctrl-b Alt-3 (main-horizontal)
- Ctrl-b Alt-4 (main-vertical)
- Ctrl-b Alt-5 (tiled)

